# virtual event platform

A web application designed for managing virtual events, including features such as user registration, event scheduling, and participation management.

# Features
User Authentication: Secure registration and login system with JWT token-based authentication.
Event Management: Create, update, and delete events.
Participant Management: Users can register for events and manage their participation.

# Technologies Used
Node.js: Server-side JavaScript runtime.
Express: Web framework for building RESTful APIs
JWT: For secure user authentication.

